        Public Sub GetNamedSelectionFromServer(ByVal SelectedNameRowId As Long, ByVal SelectedNamecolumnId As Long, ByVal SelectedNameTableImportId As Long)
        Details:

        'Function : GetNamedSelectionFromServer
        'Functionality : To make server call to servlet xlNamedSelectionService and return the Cell information (rowid and colid)
        ' that are part of Markup Range assigned for the given cell. The Userid, Rowid, Columnid and Tableid are passed as parameters
        ' to this servlet. The returned information is processed and Markup Range is highlighted
